snippet.title: HeadHorse Legacy v2.0 Available
snippet.description:
HeadHorse Legacy v2.0 is now available for download on Android and iOS. Download it now and try to escape from the most diabolical killer!

Play Now!
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.YellowPixelGames.HeadHorse
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/headhorse-horror-game/id1498926442

Join our Discord group and participate with feedback and ideas. Click the link below.

Social networks, Discord and games! Click on the link.
https://linktr.ee/yellowpixel

HeadHorse Reborn has not been cancelled, more news about that in the future.
